TieIVMDqkhxHnxAM=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="0d0915c3-567c-4527-ba1f-0362e1bce1ca"><source>Select your charging time from the recommended period, and tap the <x id="3" /> button or reply <x id="4" /> to Smart PV Assistant.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="5">Select your charging time from the recommended period, and tap the <x id="3" /> button or reply <x id="4" /> to Smart PV Assistant.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="5">Selecteer uw oplaadtijd uit de aanbevolen periode en tik op de knop <x id="3" /> of antwoord <x id="4" /> aan Slimme PV-assistent.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="5"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">D7+v5DNhQsuk25y/Gri4UBd6aOA=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="8e1b5b9e-5d1d-47ad-9ae3-afd20d8d1113"><source>Smart PV Assistant will create a charging plan based on your selection.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="6">Smart PV Assistant will create a charging plan based on your selection.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="6">Slimme PV-assistent maakt een laadschema op basis van uw selectie.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="6"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">mc5n/SfC4QlK0Fgwy/JojrtG9mE=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="c5619f93-f8a0-4648-a7a1-73e3269dd91f"><source>Start charging:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="7">Start charging:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="7">Begin met opladen</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="7"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">3Amo+zLRSLm7vw36V9VmmGll89I=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="8690a9f3-e93b-49f5-941d-a267a3b5382d"><source>Insert the charging connector completely into the charger and the vehicle.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="8">Insert the charging connector completely into the charger and the vehicle.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="8">Plaats de laadaansluiting volledig in de oplader en de laadpoort van het voertuig.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="8"><sdl:rep id="n3PROUUu+qwM2qS8Tpss8KTvBtE=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">n3PROUUu+qwM2qS8Tpss8KTvBtE=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="380a1566-e9de-4f59-881a-943fa0b3eb21"><source>On the charger screen, tap <g id="8"><x id="6" /></g>.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="9">On the charger screen, tap <g id="8"><x id="6" /></g>.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="9">Tik op <g id="8"><x id="6" /></g> op het scherm van de oplader.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="9"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">Ukb4GQfFkwsZjoqB4ycxdPj+6Nw=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="45c297d1-ac71-4601-86b8-ee41e9b382e4"><source>Tap <x id="13" />.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="10">Tap <x id="13" />.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="10">Tik op <x id="13" />.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="10"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">2vfU7d6NV/fv9J5IvK5cNrpU8Z8=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="d1cddea4-ab57-4369-b7d9-52b3097a1b15"><source>If the indicator on the charger turns blue on and off cyclically (on for 4s and off for 1s), the charger is in the scheduled charging waiting state.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="11">If the indicator on the charger turns blue on and off cyclically (on for 4s and off for 1s), the charger is in the scheduled charging waiting state.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="11">Als de indicator op de oplader cyclisch blauw knippert (4 s aan en 1 s uit), bevindt de oplader zich in de geplande wachtstand voor opladen.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="11"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">D54+7ywf4OX8+gDD8btZTKhE8QY=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="40063718-c223-4726-9354-535dec0a828c"><source>Charging will automatically start at the specified time.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="12">Charging will automatically start at the specified time.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="12">Opladen begint automatisch op het geplande tijdstip</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="12"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">Wwci/8KPtM82ZeuK7QnJEVPxQes=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="b5d693ad-c7fa-4257-924d-31a6ae120c6f"><source>To use the smart suggestions for scheduled charging, the plant must have been running for more than seven days.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="13">To use the smart suggestions for scheduled charging, the plant must have been running for more than seven days.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="13">Om de slimme suggesties voor gepland opladen te kunnen gebruiken, moet de installatie langer dan zeven dagen in bedrijf zijn geweest.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="13"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">fVNwRhj9niwAYi93EVDtSwdqd2w=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="fba98130-527a-43d7-bb6b-0379352edfbf"><source>The system will analyze historical running data accordingly and provide recommended policies.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="14">The system will analyze historical running data accordingly and provide recommended policies.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="14">Het systeem analyseert de historische werkingsgegevens dienovereenkomstig en biedt aanbevolen beleidsregels.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="14"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">m8zg3rx6U7N5/p/I2ySaWvKwzmA=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="6dda8214-94f1-48e8-bbed-35cc6934fff0"><source>The savings are intelligently estimated based on the charging records, PV+battery running status, and electricity price trend.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="15">The savings are intelligently estimated based on the charging records, PV+battery running status, and electricity price trend.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="15">De besparingen worden intelligent geschat op basis van de oplaadrecords, de werkingsstatus van PV+batterij en de trend van de elektriciteitsprijzen.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="15"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">dQ77VCf5JVj6hwioiVqloXk7NiE=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="83584358-4b4c-40ef-b30c-d6c5603fa0be"><source>The actual savings are affected by weather and electricity consumption.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="16">The actual savings are affected by weather and electricity consumption.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="16">De werkelijke besparingen worden beïnvloed door weer en elektriciteitsverbruik.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="16"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">0mI7MDl+6hA/YBceAewFZHb6HSk=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="a1d54228-0f5d-406f-b740-03935251cdb2"><source>The recommended time is set based on historical charging duration and does not guarantee a full charge.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="17">The recommended time is set based on historical charging duration and does not guarantee a full charge.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="17">De aanbevolen tijd is ingesteld op basis van de historische oplaadduur en biedt geen garantie op een volledige lading.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="17"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">sQHDZp9MPvtuPVPDjDUU/Ys1rqg=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="bf30bdb6-0b50-464b-8d6b-1b9d205867bc"><source>It is recommended that you flexibly adjust the scheduled charging based on your actual requirements, to achieve the best experience.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="18">It is recommended that you flexibly adjust the scheduled charging based on your actual requirements, to achieve the best experience.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="18">Het wordt aanbevolen om het geplande opladen flexibel aan te passen op basis van uw werkelijke vereisten, om de beste ervaring te verkrijgen.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="18"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">vceJPsHc/6RrRlM/AjAR4pilyaM=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="e05c2e91-5f44-44e1-abf5-45585be50847"><source>Fast Charging</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="19">Fast Charging</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="19">Snel laden</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="19"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">lubC/BS0hI76rhELSPBmG38/jrM=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="2f3a693a-52ef-4eae-84f3-3a92409445a0"><source>Insert the charging connector completely into the charger and the vehicle.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="20">Insert the charging connector completely into the charger and the vehicle.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="20">Steek de laadconnector volledig in de lader en het voertuig.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="20" locked="true"><sdl:rep id="n3PROUUu+qwM2qS8Tpss8KTvBtE=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">n3PROUUu+qwM2qS8Tpss8KTvBtE=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="d4b19b2c-ee70-4d76-883a-dd98527792c7"><source>Send an instruction to Smart PV Assistant, for example, tap <x id="15" />.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="21">Send an instruction to Smart PV Assistant, for example, tap <x id="15" />.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="21">Stuur een instructie naar Slimme PV-assistent, bijvoorbeeld door op <x id="15" /> te tikken.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="21"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">QeuW7wiAmfHsOXs193V0cVJ5naM=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="013abf09-d36f-4fde-bc7b-5ae0682e4651"><source>After Smart PV Assistant responds with the charging plan, tap <x id="16" /> to start charging.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="22">After Smart PV Assistant responds with the charging plan, tap <x id="16" /> to start charging.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="22">Nadat Slimme PV-assistent met het laadschema reageert, tikt u op <x id="16" /> om het opladen te starten.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="22"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">PSUrOw1B2gYcXB1UN2mBtKA5eDU=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="077b8745-fb17-4b21-ae52-d3333644ece8"><source>Stopping Charging</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="23">Stopping Charging</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="23">Opladen stoppen</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="23"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">S0ugHPU1pe2VU/OR53UTXTu7als=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="b48b141c-a0c0-4bdf-9382-2d3ce0b43eaf"><source>Press and hold <x id="17" /> on the app to stop charging.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="24">Press and hold <x id="17" /> on the app to stop charging.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="24">Druk in de app op <x id="17" /> en blijf ingedrukt houden om het opladen te stoppen.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="24"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">FOLJCfr6g1O/Ih9Mo3YsZIGjPm8=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="6bbeb381-7567-47a5-899c-9faee0443251"><source>Swipe the RFID card in the swiping area to stop charging.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="25">Swipe the RFID card in the swiping area to stop charging.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="25">U kunt ook de RFID-kaart bij het swipe-gedeelte houden om het opladen te stoppen.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="25"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">HURbVd5j4lvmGQtQUovawcPWWBs=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group></body></file></xliff>